
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>A Cozy Corner for Riya</title>
    <style>
        body {
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #dbe9f4, #fce4ec);
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px;
            color: #4a4a4a;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #ff6f91;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .gif {
            width: 300px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin: 15px auto;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }
        .hug-btn {
            padding: 12px 25px;
            background-color: #ffb6b9;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 18px;
            cursor: pointer;
            color: white;
            transition: 0.3s ease;
        }
        .hug-btn:hover {
            background-color: #ff7a85;
        }
        .popup {
            display: none;
            font-size: 20px;
            margin-top: 15px;
            color: #7d5a50;
        }
        audio {
            margin-top: 25px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Hi Riya 🌧️🍫</h1>
    <p>ik i am not there with u rn but i tried something hope u like it</p>
    <p>— from kkabir 🫶</p>

    <img class="gif" src="https://media.giphy.com/media/GeimqsH0TLDt4tScGw/giphy.gif" alt="Panda GIF">
    <img class="gif" src="https://media.giphy.com/media/YTbZzCkRQCEJa/giphy.gif" alt="Chocolate GIF">
